		A "TRIVIAL" (lol) AUTOTOOLS HELLO WORLD

INTRODUCTION
------------

This directory contains examples of GNU Autotools usage.

In order to work out the exercises you will need 

  autotools (autoconf, automake, libtool and friends)
  autotoconf archive (*)


(*) This is for AX_PTHREAD() m4 macro. Alternatively, you may donwload it by 
    following the link in this page: 
    http://www.gnu.org/software/autoconf-archive/ax_pthread.html

CONTENTS
--------

  proj-000      A simple project notu using autotools
  proj-001	A minimal autotools example
  proj-002      Using subdirs plus config.h and init flags
  proj-003      Bulding and installing libraries
  proj-004      Using configurantion tests, replacements

